        public static final org.stringtemplate.v4.misc.MultiMap<java.lang.Integer,​java.lang.Integer> validImportTypes
        Set of valid imports. Maps delegate to set of delegator grammar types. validDelegations.get(LEXER) gives list of the kinds of delegators that can import lexers.

      • checkAssocElementOption

        public boolean checkAssocElementOption
        When this is true, the semantic checks will report ErrorType.UNRECOGNIZED_ASSOC_OPTION where appropriate. This may be set to false to disable this specific check.

        The default value is true.
